Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只剩本艦跟GunBuster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GunBuster如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與敵方主力交戰中 正陷入苦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中 對方太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下撐不過2分鐘了 一定得抓到他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慣性消除器 全開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 想死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…史密斯… 請你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到你了
